1. *Oluje* su pogodile grad i uzrokovale veliku štetu. (Storms* have hit the city and caused great damage.)
2. Nadamo se da *oluja* neće ometati naš plan puta. (We hope that the *storm* won't interfere with our travel plans.)
3. Stanovnici obalnog područja evakuisani su zbog najavljenih *olujnih* udara. (Coastal residents were evacuated due to the announced *storm* gusts.)
4. Nakon *oluje* na putu su ostale velike količine otpada. (After the *storm,* large amounts of debris remained on the road.)
5. *Oluja* se bliži, treba da se pripremimo. (The *storm* is approaching, we need to prepare.)
6. Pad temperature pratio je jak *olujni* vetar. (A drop in temperature was accompanied by strong *stormy* winds.)
7. *Oluja* je uzburkala more i izazvala velike talase. (The *storm* stirred up the sea and caused large waves.)
8. Čim je počela *oluja,* nestalo je struje. (As soon as the *storm* started, the power went out.)
9. Avionski saobraćaj je obustavljen zbog *olujnih* uslova. (Air traffic was suspended due to *stormy* conditions.)
10. Kiša i *oluja* nisu nas sprečile da se zabavimo na rođendanskoj proslavi. (Rain and *storm* didn't stop us from having fun at the birthday party.)